      <p class="text-neutral-900 lg:text-lg">
        Never stop Fueling Your Passion & Performance. Get fresh supply delivered to your door, and enjoy Long Run
        Coffee membership status.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 lg:gap-4">
        <div>
          <img
            src="{{ "img-home-box.png" | asset_url }}"
